影片原计划在2007年发行，其后推迟到2008年，再到2009年，最终定在2010年发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cinema.fluctuat.net/blog/35857-cherie-je-t-emmene-voir-wikipedia-au-cine-.html|access-date=2010-11-10|language=fr|website=Les news cinéma de fluctuat.net|date=2009-02-05|title=Chérie, je t'emmène voir Wikipedia au ciné !|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723130605/http://cinema.fluctuat.net/blog/35857-cherie-je-t-emmene-voir-wikipedia-au-cine-.html|archive-date=2011-07-23}}</ref>。部分内容于2007年在[[台北市|台北市]][[维基媒体国际会议|维基媒体国际会议]]抢先公开<ref name="cheersandboos">{{cite web|url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/08/04/cheers-and-boos-as-wikipedians-see-themselves-on-film/|title=Cheers and Boos as Wikipedians See Themselves on Film|last=Cohen|first=Noam|date=2007-08-04|website=The New York Times|access-date=2010-10-26|archive-date=2012-04-25|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67CNJVIW5?url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/08/04/cheers-and-boos-as-wikipedians-see-themselves-on-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，获得编辑群体褒贬不一的评价<ref name="cheersandboos" />。2008年，维基媒体基金会在影片筹款活动的宣传视频中公开部分片段<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lUy3eP1BBM|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210520094800/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lUy3eP1BBM|archive-date= 2021-05-20|url-status= no|title= Free Access To All Human Knowledge, A Video Appeal From Wikipedia Founder Jimmy Wales|author= Wikimedia Foundation|author-link= Wikimedia Foundation|date= October 2008|publisher= YouTube|access-date= 2010-11-28}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。影片最终于2010年7月在[[格但斯克|格但斯克]]维基媒体国际会议上首映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://trojmiasto.gazeta.pl/trojmiasto/1,35636,8118873,Gdansk__Rusza_swiatowy_zjazd_Wikipedystow.html|access-date=2010-11-10|title=Gdańsk. Rusza światowy zjazd Wikipedystów|website=Gazeta Wyborcza|date=2010-07-08|first=Izabela|last=Jopkiewicz|language=pl|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610195706/http://trojmiasto.gazeta.pl/trojmiasto/1,35636,8118873,Gdansk__Rusza_swiatowy_zjazd_Wikipedystow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约300名观众到场观看<ref name="hamann" </><ref>{{cite web | url = http://wikimania2010.wikimedia.org/wiki/Truth_in_Numbers%3F | title = Truth in Numbers? | work = Wikimania 2010 | access-date = 2010-10-27 | archive-date = 2021-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518105142/https://wikimania2010.wikimedia.org/wiki/Truth_in_Numbers%3F | dead-url = no }}</ref>。影片预告片于2010年10月公开<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.trailerdownload.net/movie/truth-in-numbers/trailers/trailer-4680.html | title = Truth in numbers trailer | work = Trailerdownload.net | access-date = 2010-10-29 | year = 2010 | url-status = dead | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101101104123/http://www.trailerdownload.net/movie/truth-in-numbers/trailers/trailer-4680.html | archive-date = 2010-11-01 }}</ref>。

2010年10月20日，影片在[[纽约|纽约]]{{tsl|en|Paley Center for Media|佩利媒体中心}}放映<ref name="paleycenter">{{cite web | url = http://www.paleycenter.org/paleydocfest2010-truth-in-numbers-everything-according-to-wikipedia | title = Truth in Numbers? Everything, According to Wikipedia | work = The Paley Center for Media | year = 2010 | access-date = 2022-03-18 | archive-date = 2010-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100925202622/http://www.paleycenter.org/paleydocfest2010-truth-in-numbers-everything-according-to-wikipedia | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0960864/|title=Release info|website=Internet Movie Database|year=2010|access-date=2022-03-18|archive-date=2022-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220215034151/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0960864/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，列入罗伯特·M·巴查大学系列研讨会环节<ref name="paleycenter" />。期间，佩里中心在网上转播活动，是首次在线下线上同步举行影片放映与小组答问环节<ref name="spiers">{{cite web|title=American Premiere of 'Wikipedia' Movie Will Also Stream Online|first=Katherine|last=Spiers|date=2010-10-19|website=The Wrap|url=http://www.thewrap.com/media/article/american-premiere-wikipedia-movie-will-also-stream-online-21818|access-date=2010-11-10|archive-date=2015-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611231110/http://www.thewrap.com/media/article/american-premiere-wikipedia-movie-will-also-stream-online-21818/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2010/10/20/paley_center_and_snagfilms_stream_live_doc_debut/|access-date=2010-11-10|title=Paley Center and SnagFilms Stream Live Doc Debut|website=Digital Future|publisher=IndieWire|date=2010-10-20|first=Anne|last=Thompson|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125172854/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/2010/10/20/paley_center_and_snagfilms_stream_live_doc_debut|archive-date=2010-11-25}}</ref>。小组讨论由《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》记者诺姆·科恩（Noam Cohen）主持，影片导演、[[维基媒体基金会|维基媒体基金会]]代表塞缪尔·克莱因（Samuel Klein）与大英博物馆{{tsl|en|Wikipedian in Residence|驻点维基人}}连姆·怀亚特（Liam Wyatt）出席<ref name="spiers" />。活动介绍后，“SnagFilms”为美国地区观众免费上线影片六天<ref name="spiers" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Snag Truth By Numbers on October 21|first=Jennifer|last=Merin|date=2010-10-20|website=Documentaries Guide|publisher=The New York Times Company|url=http://documentaries.about.com/b/2010/10/20/snag-truth-by-numbers-on-october-21.htm|access-date=2010-11-11|archive-date=2010-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101025045730/http://documentaries.about.com/b/2010/10/20/snag-truth-by-numbers-on-october-21.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

